    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "There is a feature in Claude that most users never turn on \u2014 and it's the most powerful thing Anthropic shipped this year.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5001c5bb2b1a13a78184b3d5218568ba6d9125c8d649e95b9160f3e4bebf09e8",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 6.733786848072563,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "It's called Connectors. And right now, 375 integrations are sitting in your settings, waiting.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0e4ff568b1600fe47acbf52d164395c4bd07244f63cf8734495950b92a2f04cd",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 6.176507936507937,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 23
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Without Connectors, Claude only knows what you paste in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5c093bb66f06dbc0a0f457dadf5c1d58372a4aca57ca04eccd308222189c8e1",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 37
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "With them, Claude reads your Google Drive, scans your Gmail, browses your GitHub repositories, and checks your Slack messages \u2014 in real time, without you copying a single thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1eb3f48fe98b5ace96a20d2f4a051bf8e47a0a42bd3254d3633947e6946ec544",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 11.331337868480725,
      "word_count": 29,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Here is how it works. Claude Connectors run on M C P \u2014 the Model Context Protocol \u2014 an open standard that lets Claude reach into your tools through a secure, permission-controlled tunnel.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56cae1b12b58d8b69be2cf6c182b271457d6c8d186e884dd8f3d15387fc114eb",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 12.027936507936507,
      "word_count": 33,
      "words_offset": 75
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "You authorize once, and Claude can pull the data whenever you ask.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4ce5b85f54d5879db86e028917b9806dfa38c2ddfc3cc66ee52dadba0e02f11a",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 108
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Your files never leave your accounts. Claude only reads what you explicitly ask it to look at in that conversation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f4e7cbfb6c1014dc759dd3bc15068471d2c16a3789bf11a14c2186d8c9854182",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 7.337505668934241,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 120
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Now let's talk about the three workflows that actually change your daily work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8760c1d5b3afafa5409516aa195018611a30d9508f6ae4b1a0beb72558427a55",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Workflow one: document synthesis. You have a project scattered across five Drive files, three emails, and a Slack thread.",
      "checksum": "sha256:caf8d22d5df0c5fa911b916e5264efa39cbf801541c70c38d46b7e3a6784511c",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 7.244625850340136,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 153
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Normally you'd spend 30 minutes copying context into a chat window.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e8eae70d70c8592e66c74b565a8678ea09f7935236e99aaaee0ea7513e5b16b",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 172
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "With Google Drive and Gmail Connectors running, you describe the project in one sentence and Claude surfaces the relevant documents, extracts the key decisions, and delivers a summary.",
      "checksum": "sha256:877dd503c849d39da7c7ba2d3ea6311e780498e6a570078b81d7f70bc2c0417f",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 10.588299319727891,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 183
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "What took 30 minutes takes 90 seconds. Workflow two: code review with full context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4287b4979db2f07f7b30d3cddd7f9d2d371dead1bd398cc4d0185f68d5e88a50",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 5.944308390022676,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 211
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Connect GitHub and ask Claude to review a pull request.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d11f4d0cb1ae4357fc184bdcf40fe91b759054dac9e8c2f2f33ecc0568b732f7",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 225
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Claude reads the diff, traces the functions back through the repository, checks whether the implementation matches the comments in the issue, and flags anything inconsistent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e27de4bc7c6c1ed5f314a0a6cf301d0a0b31bab410b87515d180b3eea5fd09da",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 9.7059410430839,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 235
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "No repository cloning. No pasting diffs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dfb302e94cb415f8d5a4f76490bcfb66f6002ea7dcc6fe7a20e8e8cece1fd222",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 260
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Full codebase context, available in the conversation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c739876c78ec169c65c4b8b0ef88b207e9b02050904566a4175d572d260eff43",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 266
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Workflow three: background agents. This is the newest and least-known part.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d26ce94a8b66c2038e7798ca4bdcbfdbf27689299e51f202688c82a98336d064",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 273
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Claude Managed Agents \u2014 launched in April 2026 \u2014 let Connectors run in the background.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e3652278ffebb70a5c3ae9a9c99cdde07c8474cf2e354018e26c2671591a0139",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 5.712108843537415,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 284
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "You describe a task: monitor this Slack channel, summarize every GitHub issue that comes in this week, flag any Drive document that mentions a specific client.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c9122f2b3532e33cb6bdab9b77456e1d2cca84c8fb6d145b509a243c4becf979",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 9.520181405895691,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 299
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Claude runs that as a long-lived agent, not just a one-shot chat.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2ff045f1b2d9b63173a94bcf641f188e837769d8e200857c617c34c1b54d87c4",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 325
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "You get results delivered to you. To enable all of this: open claude.ai, go to Settings, click Connectors, and browse the directory.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ee576f592d8bc8ab0a30c02c2a2529b39678b5077e94151d744079a16e64a335",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 8.6378231292517,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 337
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Connect Google Workspace, GitHub, and Slack in under two minutes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d8b58c96718ae5aa52f468297ba1e0a9b77154f973eb740811145958d4cd9a9f",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 359
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Then open any chat, tap the plus icon, and toggle the connectors for that session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3f44577b67414f155c857bad7b58e54f08af72f67dff917e5b995681a8148d42",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 369
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "375 integrations. Most users have zero enabled.\n\nQuick one before you go.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b1e955fb6f7f5b31cd0fe16455423fe4b511997412359613288d48ac9cd1a010",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 384
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Which connector are you turning on first?",
      "checksum": "sha256:07bf88663c4dd11e8252d6346c70b4ee435a808fb9860bfaa4efa61db586e1d6",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 396
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "And what's missing from the 375? Drop it in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:76e92bebe77b0f4192dad5226fcd0ab0ed3ea1df56e524e92795839ae26c058d",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 403
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous.ai community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:11103ce9f04648e297b0f9cd6e8075323647e9cb83506d3f92d6e3dcbba8e7fe",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 414
    }
  ]
}